# APEX-maintained patch against kjain14/testgeneval. The PR plan that
# tracks the upstream-merge work for this divergence lives in
# UPSTREAM_PR_PLAN.md alongside this file. See PR 1 ("--mutation_timeout"
# flag plumbing) and PR 2 ("macOS bind-mount fix"). The historical
# "--memory_swappiness 5" -> "--memory-swappiness 5" hunk has been
# removed from this patch as of Phase 1.3 because fixing the upstream
# typo silently changes container behaviour vs. the published baseline.
